{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"37232-the-bee-and-the-elephant","title":"The Bee and the Elephant","description":"An elephant tries to help a little lost bee find his home. Is it the nest? The cave? Where does he live?","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Celia  Bolam"],"illustrators":["Try Samphos"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/37232-the-bee-and-the-elephant"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101349/size3/39f8b81749a713480835e9f715fadc44.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101349/size6/39f8b81749a713480835e9f715fadc44.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70648/size6/fe1b31925af9a57a5d3a1281c6cf1cb6.jpg","text":"\"I am lost,\" said Little Bee. \"I cannot find my home!\"\n\"Can you please help me, Mr. Elephant?\"","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70649/size6/07061b321da7266072160ff876ce4e77.jpg","text":"\"Is this nest your home, Little Bee?\" the elephant asked.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70650/size6/a06af699700f20ef5140c9c956c061b0.jpg","text":"\"Oh no!\" cried Little Bee.  \n\"This is a bird’s home.\"","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70651/size6/2f10123d603f874c1ca6707aafd77f34.jpg","text":"\"Is this cave your home?\" asked the elephant.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70652/size6/84ce8fa2cec2f87c58cc550584aa8224.jpg","text":"\"Oh no! This is a bat’s home.\"","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70653/size6/4ab9a75a1bed75e484c830d3be122d5e.jpg","text":"\"Is\nthis hive your home, Little Bee?\"","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70654/size6/c00f1b52a3ffdca9896d639570d0c361.jpg","text":"\"Oh yes!\" said Little Bee happily.\n\"This is my home.\"","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70655/size6/1e1b66205e23b3bc3c1bd768aebb8dcd.jpg","text":"\"Thank\nyou for helping me, Mr. Elephant.\"","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70657/size6/bca814973ad21166be18cc2592ef9d8c.jpg","text":"10/10","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":9,"words":78}}